text: No wonder she’s been in bikinis all summer! Heidi Klum has a message to prove but her friends are not that into it. It turns out while she is one of the most renowned beauties in Hollywood and makes it look so easy, it isn’t, and behind closed doors, she makes sure those around her know it.
title: Heidi Klum's Bikini Body Takes A Lot Of Work & Her Boyfriend Is Over Hearing About It
